And I didn't even discover it until about level 30!<br>
<br>
I think hide is way better than camo for medding.  It has the same effect, doesn't cost mana, you don't have to mem it, and it doesn't wear off after a random length of time.<br>
<br>
It's especially useful for going AFK, since it never wears off unless you move, cast, or are spotted by a mob with see-invis.  Even in towns - you don't want those noobs cussing you out 'cause they saw you sat there but you didn't respond ;)  What they don't see, can't hurt them.<br>
<br>
The downside is that you have to target a mob with a view other than &quot;indifferent&quot; so you know whether it's worked, and it sometimes takes a few tries.<br>
I like a rogue's hide skill, it tells you when it works :) <p>-- <br>
